import {css} from "emotion";
 
// import {unitMath,applyUnitIfRequired} from "../../../utils/css-utils";
import styleMemoize from "../../../utils/style-memoize";
import flaggedStyles from "../../../utils/flagged-styles";
// import {unitMath} from "../../utils/css-utils";
import getMenuVars from "../menu/menu.var";
 
 
export default styleMemoize(function(flags = []) {
 
  const menuVars = getMenuVars();
 
  const {
    labelBackground,
    labelTextColor,
    labelVerticalPadding,
    labelHorizontalPadding,
  } = menuVars;
 
 
  return flaggedStyles("listview-label",flags,{
 
    _: ()=>(css`
 
      display: block;
      font-weight:normal;
      margin-left:0;
      margin-top:0;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      line-height:1.3em;
      border-radius:0.3em;
      overflow:hidden;
      text-align: center;
 
      background: ${labelBackground};
      color: ${labelTextColor};
      padding: ${labelVerticalPadding} ${labelHorizontalPadding};
 
      &.icon {
        display:inline;
      }
    `),
 
    basic: ()=>(css`
      border-style: solid;
      border-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      border-width:1px;
      background:none;
      color:inherit;
    `),
 
    "basic,left": ()=>(css`
      border-radius:0;
      border-width:0 1px 0 0;
      padding-left:0,
    `),
 
 
  });
});
